A relaxed fit gives you some room to layer up underneath for those extra chilly days.

Goose down insulation is strategically placed to keep you warm all day long.

clothes.title: PSD Men's AND1 Boxer Briefs
clothes.description: It's time to upgrade your streetwear from head to toe, starting with the freshest basics in your wardrobe - shop the iconic AND1 X PSD underwear collection. Designed for men who refuse to settle for basic, our men's boxer briefs are all about pushing boundaries and making a bold statement. Our AND1 boxer briefs are the perfect fusion of comfort, style, and attitude, featuring our latest graphic designs and our heritage trash talk quotes. Crafted with premium soft fabrics, these boxers are ready to handle your everyday hustle, while keeping you looking fly. Whether you're hitting the courts, chilling with friends, or slaying the urban scene, AND1's street apparel and underwear will have you standing out in a crowd and feeling comfortable too. So get ready to level up your fashion game, because with AND1, you'll dominate the streets with swag and style that's on a whole new level.

Casually confident and classically cool, these relaxed pants are a must-have in any wardrobe.
